cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.PF, cs.LG, cs.AI

This paper deals with the problem of energy consumption in data centers, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also proposes online algorithms for dynamic provisioning, which involves decision-making under uncertainty and optimization (cs.SY, cs.PF). The algorithms are based on mathematical models and analysis, which suggests a connection to machine learning and optimization (cs.LG, cs.AI).
